entries.title_d: Apparently the Death Star section from the freighter in the last mission pummeled through orbit and landed on Lok, still partly intact. Nym has found it and he's willing to sell it to the Alliance. You have to travel to Lok and escort the Nym smuggler transporting it to the Rebel Space station in the Lok system.
entries.title: Lok system: Escort the smuggler transporting Death Star data.

entries.quest_rendezvous_d: The Nym smuggler has provided us with these coordinates for your rendez-vous. Make haste over there.
entries.quest_location_d: You are to head to the Lok system to meet up with one of Nym's smugglers. The Lok system is relatively safe from the Empire but it's heavily inhabited by different pirate factions on the look out for a lone traveler so stay sharp!
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the Nym smuggler to the Rebel space station. Keep your eyes open, the Empire seems to be one step ahead of us through out this entire operation.
entries.panic_5: TIE's incoming, give them a warm welcome pilot!

entries.panic_3: And I was hoping we could slip out of here undetected...
entries.panic_2: Imperials, they are gunning for us!
entries.panic_1: An Imperial patrol picked us up, prepare for a fight!
entries.hull_half: I'm tracking multiple hull breaches! I can't take much more damage. Help!
